episodes.title: Scientology Piano Scam - Stephen Ridley.
episodes.description:
Look I know this is a guitar channel  but I do play piano too.
You will have seen Stephen Ridley pop up in ads before videos here on YouTube. 
He tells you that you can learn piano really quickly and easily and it's free. 
Except you can't and it isn't.
And as we all know after the Ken Tamplin thing, I'm not a huge fan of liars. 
So today we'll take a look at Stephen Ridley and his over priced piano course and I'll explain why I have an issue with this.
I'll also tell you how you can actually learn piano for a fraction of the cost  of his course. 
I also left you a little video right at the ned as an extra bonus. 
Thanks for watching and don't forget to like and subscribe.
